text: Comeback is the fourth and final studio album by German all-female pop-rap band Tic Tac Toe, released in 2006 by A One Entertainment. The album was their first in nearly a decade recorded in the original line-up, after Ricarda "Ricky" Wältken had re-joined the band. The album was preceded by the single "Spiegel" in 2005 which became a top 10 hit in German-speaking countries. However, the second and final single, "Keine Ahnung", was a commercial failure and did not enter any charts.
